-- Expedia corporate arm launches China service
-- 
-- Tue Nov 27, 2007 4:15am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/11/27/us-expedia-china-idUSSHA29880920071127

 

 SHANGHAI (Reuters) -Expedia Inc's corporate travel agency plans to start up a service in China by partnering with the country's second-largest online travel firm, eLong Inc, the companies said on Tuesday. 

 The tie-up with Beijing-based eLong is the first foray into Asia for Expedia Corporate Travel, which has operations in the United States, Canada, France, the United Kingdom, Belgium, Germany, Italy and Spain, the companies said in a statement. (Reporting by  Sophie Taylor ; Editing by Anne Marie Roantree)